^^ Session based testing

* <b>Charter</b> - a goal or agenda for a test session.

* <b>Session</b> - an uninterrupted period of time spent testing, ideally lasting one to two hours.

* Each session is focused on a charter, but not restricted to it.

* The tester creates and executes tests based on ideas or heuristics and records their progress.

